 {\textbackslash}usepackage\{amsbsy\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{mathrsfs\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{upgreek\} {\textbackslash}setlength\{{\textbackslash}oddsidemargin\}\{-69pt\} {\textbackslash}begin\{document\}\$\${\textbackslash}upgamma\$\${\textbackslash}end\{document\}, n)225Ra -{\textgreater}beta-{\textbackslash}documentclass[12pt]\{minimal\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{amsmath\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{wasysym\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{amsfonts\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{amssymb\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{amsbsy\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{mathrsfs\} {\textbackslash}usepackage\{upgreek\} {\textbackslash}setlength\{{\textbackslash}oddsidemargin\}\{-69pt\} {\textbackslash}begin\{document\}\$\${\textbackslash}stackrel\{\{{\textbackslash}upbeta \}{\textless}{\textasciicircum}{\textgreater}\{-\}\}\{{\textbackslash}to \}\$\${\textbackslash}end\{document\}225Ac approach.},
